- [x] `ProvidersController` — 12 `.block()` → 10s BLOCK_TIMEOUT
- [x] `AdminKnowledgeController` — 12 `.block()` → 10s BLOCK_TIMEOUT
- [x] `CommandController`, `SystemMonitoringController` — BLOCK_TIMEOUT
