### 🟠 P1 — HIGH: Provider List Caching (Performance)
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

- [ ] **`MultiAIVotingService.executeMainFlow()`** — প্রতি request এ:
      `providerRepository.findAll()` + `firebaseRealtimeService.getData()` দুটো I/O কল
      **সমাধান:** Redis-এ 30s TTL দিয়ে active provider list cache করুন:
