## 🎯 পরবর্তী অ্যাকশন (অগ্রাধিকার অনুযায়ী)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

**এখনই (P0 Critical):**
  ① `AutomaticTaskAssigner` — `blockLast()` + ১১ `.block()` → reactive redesign
  ② `AIFallbackOrchestrator` + `ThirdOpinionOrchestrator` — 60s `.block()` → 15s
  ③ `ProviderCapabilityAnalyzer` — 60s `.block()` + unbounded `.block()` ফিক্স
  ④ `ProviderHealingStrategies` — unbounded `.block()` (২টো) → bounded timeout
  ⑤ `SupremeLearningOrchestrator` — unbounded `.block()` → `block(10s)`

**এই সপ্তাহে (P1 High):**
  ⑥ ~~`AIProviderFactory` health cache → Caffeine~~ ✅ সম্পন্ন
  ⑦ active provider list Redis caching (30s TTL) — MultiAIVotingService + GracefulDegradation
  ⑧ `UsageOptimizationService` model-tier/response cache → Caffeine ✅ সম্পন্ন
  ⑨ ~~`SystemAutoDetectService` truly non-blocking health check~~ ✅ সম্পন্ন

**পরের সপ্তাহে (P2 Medium):**
  ⑩ `VisionService.analyzeScreenshot()` legacy wrapper সরান
  ⑪ `VertexAIEmbeddingService` secret → PostConstruct
  ⑫ Integration test coverage ৪০% → ৬০%
  ⑬ OpenTelemetry + Prometheus custom metrics

